##                                                                         ##
##                    COMPILER SETTINGS (VC COMPILER)                      ##
##                                                                         ##
## ======================================================================= ##


   ifeq (${COMPILER}, VC)


      ## DEFINITION OF STANDARD COMPILER SYNTAX:
      ## -----------------------------------------------------------------

